      "title": "Premium Income Corporation Announces Semi-Annual Results",
      "summary": "TORONTO, June 26, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- (TSX: PIC.A; PIC.PR.A) Premium Income Corporation (the 'Fund”) announces results of operations for the six months ended April 30, 2026. Increase in net assets attributable to holders of Class A shares amounted to $69.8 million or $3.91 per Class A share. Net assets attributable to holders of Class A shares as at April 30, 2026 were $229.4 million or $12.39 per Class A share ($11.26 per Class A share after giving effect to the May 2026 Share Split). Cash distributions of $0.64 per Preferred share and $0.52 per Class A share were paid during the period.",
